oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Republic at the Ryman with Tulip & Garland
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Ryman Auditorium (Nashville, Tenn.)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (black and green on white) Hatch poster announcing Republic at the Ryman showing with images past and present featuring Tulip & Garland. Inseparately linked with country music, the Ryman or the Mother Church of Country Music was renovated in 1994 to its original splendor.
